# Rigs of Rods

[[!img rigs-of-rods-logo.png alt="Rigs of Rods logo" size=256x256 class="projectlogo" link="no"]]

[Rigs of Rods](https://www.rigsofrods.org/) is a free and open source vehicle simulator that uses soft-body physics to simulate the motion destruction and deformation of vehicles.

